{"tid":2497113,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE新歌MV曝光！子瑜「露背裝+雙馬尾」甜翻粉絲","createTime":"2021-04-20T09:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T13:51:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"76d68270bd73b86a56c01a468b6cfa28a39f3bef","tid":2497113,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"韓國高人氣女團twice近期積極宣傳5月即將推出的日文單曲《KURA KURA》，昨（19日）在官方社群公開全新預告短片，雖然短短的30秒還聽不出整體的感覺，不過可以從短片中看見每一位成員在MV中的造型，其中讓人眼睛一亮的是周子瑜的「露背裝」，加上雙馬尾，散發出清爽又甜美的氣質，讓網友直呼好期待！<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/26/3083767-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F26%2F3083767-PH.jpg&h=b1dce775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE新專輯造型曝光。（圖／翻攝自jypetwice_japan IG）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE將在5月推全新日文單曲《KURA KURA》，昨（19日）在官方社群公開全新預告短片，讓網友看了十分期待。預告中只見成員開心地喝著下午茶，每個人服裝都別有一番風味。其中Mina、志效、彩瑛與Momo運用襯衫內搭連身裙，撞色效果十足，娜璉與Sana則以紅色系的針織上衣襯出白皙膚色，多賢胸前挖空的短版上衣露出性感的小蠻腰，定延則是穿出一身復古氣質，而子瑜的服裝最受焦點，以彩色橫條「露背裝」展現出誘人的肩頸、鎖骨，再配上可愛的雙馬尾，散發出甜美氣質。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/20/3119233-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F20%2F3119233-PH.jpg&h=76a139c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜的服裝最受焦點，以彩色橫條「露背裝」展現出誘人的肩頸、鎖骨。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE在近期又傳出在6月時會以完整體回歸韓文專輯的消息，讓粉絲們為之瘋狂，雖然確切日期尚未定案，不過成員都正積極準備，已經前往濟州島拍攝MV，真讓粉絲迫不及待！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/20/3119234-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F20%2F3119234-PH.jpg&h=5f9a2c41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE官方昨（19日）公布日文單曲《KURA KURA》預告。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）"},{"pid":"3b05e66b86dcede1d5f26969000710a65bd78940","tid":2497113,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"終於唔係暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517b1335985eba0282fff83124b0f96e309ea208","tid":2497113,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b05e66b86dcede1d5f26969000710a65bd78940","tid":2497113,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"終於唔係暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:49:59.000Z","msg":"内心暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d567bfb604a5d4d076104dfe99fdd4f5e0a7a6","tid":2497113,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"唔準視姦我老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e49ce918d16e3cad165a138cfb75c617bca684e","tid":2497113,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"41d567bfb604a5d4d076104dfe99fdd4f5e0a7a6","tid":2497113,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"唔準視姦我老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"你姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a3e4162dbadc45becf4d27a61624eb1e8a53ed","tid":2497113,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQPyrV9mcfm3oxMekjHGgxjkQovAyxHcSq5Bw55R4CHjX?filename=9vsDJxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vsDJxN.jpg&h=819eb367&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUenDZjzP4BFcQa3UULqiJJ8aVxJmecqWyusqnuxRSGg4?filename=CPmheEs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCPmheEs.jpg&h=bc1